Package: scrutin
Title: RStudio Add-In for the Scrutin Test Runner
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Vincent", "Arel-Bundock", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "vincent.arel-bundock@umontreal.ca")
Description: Launches the scrutin web dashboard inside the RStudio Viewer
    pane. Spawns 'scrutin -r web' as a background process with watch mode
    and displays the live test results in the IDE.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    later,
    processx,
    rstudioapi
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
